title: Pre-UFYB 4: Overcoming Overwhelm
itunes:title: Pre-UFYB 4: Overcoming Overwhelm
description:
As lawyers, we’re no strangers to feeling overwhelmed by our workload and doing our best to balance it with our social, family, and personal lives.

In this episode, I share my process for managing overwhelm, calming yourself down quickly, and setting yourself up for success.

Get full show notes, resources, and more information here: http://bit.ly/2pucsK3
